{"tid":1044742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英認為理大未報警已非「去得好盡」　學生感以前美好是「被洗腦」","createTime":"2019-03-03T06:20:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T16:33:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b075d29c57fd7b07988c7c215dce63595f9d7c6b","tid":1044742,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/03125028/image1551588565172.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F03125028%2Fimage1551588565172.png&h=af42b785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片來源：蘋果日報）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n理工大學民主牆去年10月初被人以紅紙遮蓋，部分學生會成員闖入校長辦公室樓層，要求與校方對話。經記律聆訊後，校方最終勒令碩士生何俊謙退學、前學生會會長林穎恆停學一年、另外兩人則被判社會服務令。為理大前身理工學院畢業生的全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英昨晚於其社交網站發文，指理大未報警已非「去得好盡」。<br />\n<br />\n對於何俊謙說「我哋只係想香港好似以前咁美好，有言論自由」，梁振英形容「這是年輕人被洗腦後的荒謬」，認為何口中的「以前」是指回歸前，反問「你知道回歸前的『自由』是什麼一回事嗎？」他提到當年學生示威時，被「港英的洋警官」打到血流披面，但警官沒有被起訴或懲處。他續指，過去港英警隊有政治部，並有專門囚禁毋須審訊的政治犯的地方，反問「你有考慮找他們談談『以前』的『美好』嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n對於泛民指理大在此事上「去得好盡」，梁振英認為「錯了，還未報警呢！」，並稱泛民常「攪私人起訴」，反問是否應用泛民思維，將何告到法庭，由法庭還他清白。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/270714/梁振英認為理大未報警已非「去得好盡」%E3%80%80學生感/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F270714%2F%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E8%AA%8D%E7%82%BA%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%AA%E5%A0%B1%E8%AD%A6%E5%B7%B2%E9%9D%9E%E3%80%8C%E5%8E%BB%E5%BE%97%E5%A5%BD%E7%9B%A1%E3%80%8D%25E3%2580%2580%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%84%9F%2F&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyELnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=95605f62\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/270714/梁振英認為理大未報警已非「去得好盡」%E3%80%80學生感/</a>"},{"pid":"5652cd1795c041fce99870e4af496548fea7219f","tid":1044742,"uid":24140,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:33:44.000Z","msg":"佢想講當年67果班?"},{"pid":"fdc4716069bdbfafe10a3b389574fe0914b4f4f6","tid":1044742,"uid":130695,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:38:33.000Z","msg":"呢條廢老成日出黎刷存在感做咩"},{"pid":"4d8674dce18bfd83c65752815b31aeb042fb0498","tid":1044742,"uid":103156,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:38:43.000Z","msg":"放炸彈嘅中共共産黨匪暴徒"},{"pid":"2834c9cf6bc50f551fbfb0f3ffe03b98b10a00bc","tid":1044742,"uid":103156,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:42:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/144140_8c7b3087e61d38dd6ecc0e6e8c45237c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F144140_8c7b3087e61d38dd6ecc0e6e8c45237c.jpg&h=8b7e42e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3d9537d183ad71123ddaf9cd343898a35bd86ac","tid":1044742,"uid":103156,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/144254_b68fc84a507fb216e436d8536f0a8cab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F144254_b68fc84a507fb216e436d8536f0a8cab.jpg&h=0c7244eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aae62a225cbf216c673e10ea6c08a4defd900526","tid":1044742,"uid":103156,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/144612_f1b5374284133f2f0d00abce7f1fbd15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F144612_f1b5374284133f2f0d00abce7f1fbd15.jpg&h=221c1558&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2443761de5cb4f1ca2ae3a01e941d9b064fb95c6","tid":1044742,"uid":24730,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:51:38.000Z","msg":"港獨之父最近咁多嘢講，係咪真係謀住黨主席個位？刁种睇緊啲你條靚好喎，一下唔覺意畀佢搞到各省紛紛獨立就唔係幾好啦"},{"pid":"df5490e92a7081d1d5ad8c22f30c49f3ee8c939a","tid":1044742,"uid":103156,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/03/145504_e4b6193da6131101d7ba3df76fc6fffa.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F03%2F145504_e4b6193da6131101d7ba3df76fc6fffa.jpeg&h=6850fbfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f7e7711caed09d8e22858f0c26ef368de38c65fc","tid":1044742,"uid":43842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdc4716069bdbfafe10a3b389574fe0914b4f4f6","tid":1044742,"uid":130695,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T06:38:33.000Z","msg":"呢條廢老成日出黎刷存在感做咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T07:05:45.000Z","msg":"再諗住做特首囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a54f3101f951f8714b76036094220bec86debc","tid":1044742,"uid":177856,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T07:05:51.000Z","msg":"咁啲黑社會都唔係去到好盡，佢地自己執行家法無報警，抵讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e905593d0ff2e6ff49fd5577ffb29242f9dde0a7","tid":1044742,"uid":237057,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T07:15:13.000Z","msg":"理大生做的事情是否不對？<br />\n我應為他們沒有做出任何損害理大的聲譽，他們只是表達微少的聲音都不可以；這是甚麼道理？在發達文明的國家或城市都會容許不同聲音。<br />\n現在香港的政府做了甚麼？政府常對外界是好包容不同聲音，叫個曲街啦，口講一套做另一套。今天，理大學生事件不出嚟支持，未來我們發聲的機會越嚟越少。故我明天會去撐班理生，希望有同行者見"},{"pid":"b1a27e0fc64920a94144be4a40b76c9475154daa","tid":1044742,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T07:18:49.000Z","msg":"咁幾廿年前放菠蘿果班點計先？<br />\n做到局長喎 冇vetting架？"},{"pid":"fc7b6ea6282eeee18823e28d789bd414a036aba2","tid":1044742,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T07:21:57.000Z","msg":"奴才相"},{"pid":"948f10658a21303a4200a96c9c69f710eeb1b1dd","tid":1044742,"uid":120678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T07:27:02.000Z","msg":"港英做過=岩？<br />\n人地做賊=做賊岩？<br />\n689 d垃圾邏輯"},{"pid":"7fcf0c8a24df82ff0086a264de6c3898b0a5959a","tid"